descriptionHtml:
[img]http://puu.sh/bQ4BS/aa7ff353df.png[/img]

Potato ENB is an ENB that I(Örvar "Wheeze" Arnórsson) made for myself and I'm releasing it now in order to celebrate me getting 4000 followers on my [url=http://www.twitch.tv/wheeze202]twitch channel[/url].

Not much effort has really been put into the ENB, no ENB out there really suited me so I decided to make my own. The general idea is that it's very performance based, no fancy ambient occlusion, AA, sun rays etc. And it basically keeps a vanilla look to the game but just compliments the lighting, no drastic stylistic choices.

And if you are wondering about the name: I just don't really care about the name and I named it the first thing that popped into my mind.


[b]In order to install just download the original ENB from [url=http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html]ENBSeries[/url] and extract the d3d9.dll file from the Wrapper version. Put all downloaded files and the d3d9.dll into your skyrim folder.[/b]
author: Wheeze
